If your problem is FT then by all means get the agues, but if you are looking for some armor to I would say do som LDoN's out of the BB camp. Nice armor there for only 150 points a peace. 
<br />
After that its up to you, I for one are going for the NRo armor now as the other sets not are a huge upgrade after the BB-armor ( not worht all the points ).
<br />
I could also surgest the 510 points string instru you can get in SRo LDoN's ( still good at 260%, but lost a bit of interest after the AE-nerff ).
<br />

<br />
I also charm-kitt a bit ( in POP-zones thow) and I only have FT1, I find it faster to use all my manna on charms and then simply die to get manna back. Its mutch faster xp / ( time spend) then sitting and medding all my manna up agen.
